---
title: Mexican Cauliflower Rice-Stuffed Poblanos with Guacamole & Zesty Crema
description: Poblano peppers are perfect for stuffing. They’re mild, earthy, and sweet, plus, they stay a vibrant forest green once roasted. Chock-full of savory ingredients like hearty cauliflower rice, fresh tomato, and Southwestern-style spices, these packed peppers are sure to satisfy. They’re topped with melty Monterey Jack and guacamole, then finished off with a dollop of zesty crema and a sprinkle of minced chili.
